data.description: Hurry this one will not last. Very open floor plan with great room concept and lots of windows with great views. Both master bath and kitchen have been updated. Backyard is like a mini resort with gorgeous pool and a large side yard waiting for a horse setup gazebo or a large garage workshop. This  home is ready to move into and the sellers priced it for a quick sale. Not a lot of hill side homes priced this low. Street is paved all the way to the house, last house on street for ultimate privacy. You won't want to miss this one.
